===Noun===
'''[[communist]] [[bandit]]''' (usually ''plural'' '''communist bandits''')
#A politically derogative term used by the [[Kuomintang]] of the [[Republic of China]] to refer to the Chinese communists.
===Usage note===
The Government of the Republic of China has stopped using this term. Private use of this term is also very rare now.
